%% TrustyAI Service Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL / PVC<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: TrustyAI Model Explainability
    Client->>Route: HTTPS/443 (TLS edge)
    Route->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443 (service-serving-cert)<br/>Bearer Token (SubjectAccessReview)
    KRBAC->>TAS: HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    TAS->>KServe: HTTP/HTTPS (configurable TLS)<br/>Model inference
    TAS->>DB: TCP/5432 or filesystem<br/>TLS optional, DB credentials

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: LLM Evaluation Job Execution
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMEvalPod as LMEval Pod<br/>+ Driver sidecar
    participant S3 as S3/OCI Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Create LMEvalJob CR
    K8sAPI-->>LMEvalPod: Controller creates Pod
    LMEvalPod->>KServe: HTTP/HTTPS<br/>LLM inference requests<br/>API Key / Token
    LMEvalPod->>S3: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Upload results<br/>Access Key / DockerConfig

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestration
    participant GORCH as Orchestrator<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Detectors as Detector<br/>InferenceServices

    Client->>Route: HTTPS/443 (TLS reencrypt)
    Route->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443 (service-serving-cert)<br/>Bearer Token (conditional)
    KRBAC->>GORCH: HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    GORCH->>KServe: HTTP/HTTPS (auto-detected TLS)<br/>Generation model
    GORCH->>Detectors: HTTP/HTTPS (auto-detected TLS)<br/>Content safety detection

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 4: EvalHub Evaluation Management
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MLFlow as MLFlow Server<br/>HTTPS

    Client->>Route: HTTPS/443 (TLS edge)
    Route->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443 (service-serving-cert)<br/>Bearer Token (SubjectAccessReview)
    KRBAC->>EvalHub: HTTP/8080 (127.0.0.1 only)
    EvalHub->>DB: TCP/5432<br/>TLS (Service CA)<br/>DB credentials (Secret)
    EvalHub->>MLFlow: HTTPS<br/>TLS (Service CA cert)<br/>SA projected token
